name: NodeInitializationAction
title: Google
Cloud

NodeInitializationAction
description: Specifies an executable to run on a fully configured node and a timeout period for executable completion.

returns.description: Required. Google Cloud Storage URI of executable file.
Required. Google Cloud Storage URI of executable file.

Optional. Amount of time executable has to complete. Default is
10 minutes. Cluster creation fails with an explanatory error message (the
name of the executable that caused the error and the exceeded timeout
period) if the executable is not completed at end of the timeout period.
